The paper discusses an integrated navigation solution for mobile robots using a single wheel mounted MEMS IMU. This falls under the field of robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also utilizes various constraints and algorithms to limit navigation errors, which falls under the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses field experiments and testing, which falls under the field of machine learning (cs.LG).
